text: Several Norwegian government vessels have been named FS Marjata: * FS Marjata (1951), in service with Norwegian government 1965-1976 and then to navy as HNoMS Vadsø * FS Marjata (1975), in service with Norwegian government 1976-1995, latterly as Marjata II * FS Marjata (1992) * FS Marjata (2014) Category:Ship names
title: FS Marjata
